ActFederal-Provincial Fiscal Arrangements Act
SubjectNew Housing Transition Tax and Rebate Act Administration Agreement with the Government of British Columbia
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of National Revenue, on behalf of the Government of Canada, enter into the NEW HOUSING TRANSITION TAX AND REBATE ACT ADMINISTRATION AGREEMENT with the GOVERNMENT OF BRITISH COLUMBIA in order to set out the terms and conditions and cost recovery details for administration, beginning on April 1, 2013.
